snippet.title: Legends Reborn | Developer Update | May 2023
snippet.description:
Join us for the Steam Playtest: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2219670 

In the May 8th Dev Update we talk about upcoming changes to the game, our new playtest coming up, and the overall direction that we want our game to go into the gaming space.

0:00 - General News
2:07 - Gameplay Changes
8:59 - Lore Updates

Legends Reborn: Age of Chance is a unique take on the TCG genre. The game combines elements of Team RPG battlers, the mechanics of card games, and unique card draw mechanics to deliver a fun experience. See you at the tables! #legendsreborn #cardgame #steam 

Check out the rest of our socials!
